					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p83198">Scale before padding or pad before scaling?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=83198#p83198"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sat Aug 27, 2011 6:01 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
